                        <li><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/img/service_icon_24_cdn.png"/><a target="_blank" id="mobile-services-global-cdn" href="/home/features/cdn/">虚拟网络</a></li>
